          <p>Stuck on a challenging section? Use practice mode to place checkpoints and practice specific parts of a level without restarting from the beginning. This feature helps you learn difficult sequences and improve your consistency. Practice mode is essential for mastering the more challenging levels.</p>
          
          <h2 id="customization">Customization and Unlockables</h2>
