            <li>Enjoy the colorful visuals while focusing on the rhythm</li>
            <li>Use the upbeat music to anticipate obstacle patterns</li>
            <li>Practice difficult sections in practice mode</li>
            <li>Don't rush—consistent, accurate jumps are key</li>
            <li>Take breaks to maintain focus and enjoy the game</li>
            <li>Study the colorful level designs before attempting them</li>
            <li>Remember that each attempt teaches you something valuable</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h2>Casual vs. Competitive Play</h2>
          <p>Breeze is perfect for casual play, but it also offers enough challenge for competitive players. Whether you're playing for relaxation or trying to beat all levels, Breeze delivers an engaging experience. The game scales well for different playstyles.</p>
          
